  <para>
    The <classname>enhanced</classname> <link
    linkend="Section-Output-Position"><classname>PositionOutput</classname></link>
    returns the original position of a point plus a given multiple of
    the Displacement Field.  The scale factor,
    <varname>factor</varname>, can be any real number.  Setting it to
    <userinput>1</userinput> makes the <classname>enhanced</classname>
    output identical to the <link
    linkend="Output-Position-actual"><classname>actual</classname></link>
    output, and setting it to <userinput>0</userinput> makes it
    identical to the <link
    linkend="Output-Position-original"><classname>original</classname></link>
    output.
  </para>


